<head>Locations</head>
<p>
<rs type="found"><rs type="monuList">Theatre</rs>: skene frons, northernmost chamber, doorway, on the north wall.</rs>
<rs type="origLocation">Findspot</rs>
<rs type="lastLocation">Findspot</rs>



</p>
